These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-1::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, poppy, sunflower, azalea
City: liverpool, marseilles, rome, edinburgh
1. the person traveling to liverpool is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to rome##5
2. the person who growspoppy is not the person traveling to liverpool##6
3. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
4. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
5. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
6. the person traveling to liverpool is not the person who growssunflower##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | poppy   | azalea    | orchid    | sunflower |
| Sport      | edinburgh | liverpool | rome | marseilles |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-2::.
House: victorian, gothic-revival, colonial, art-deco
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, dubstep, techno, funk
1. the fan gospel is on the far right##1
2. the gothic-revival house is somewhere to the left of the colonial house##5
3. the fan funk is somewhere to the left of the art-deco house##5
4. the gothic-revival house is not the fan dubstep##6
5. the fan funk is on the left of the colonial house##1
6. the fan gospel is on the right of the fan techno##1
7. the art-deco house is on the right of the victorian house##1
8. the colonial house is somewhere to the left of the victorian house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | gothic-revival  | colonial    | victorian | art-deco    |
| Food       | funk | dubstep | techno  | gospel |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-3::.
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, peach, tomato, corn
House: gothic-revival, craftsman, wooden, modern
1. the person eating corn is not the gothic-revival house##6
2. the craftsman house is not the person eating tomato##6
3. the wooden house is on the left or right of the person eating peach##3
4. the craftsman house is the person eating eggplant##1
5. the person eating peach is on the left of the craftsman house##1
6. the person eating eggplant is in an odd position##4
7. the gothic-revival house is on the far left or far right##3
8. the wooden house is somewhere to the left of the modern house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2        |   3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | corn       | peach  | eggplant  | tomato |
| Job        | wooden | modern | craftsman | gothic-revival  |

