.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, martial-arts, drama, mystery
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, june, may, august
1. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
2. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in february##5
3. the person who's birthday is in august is not the person watching martial-arts movies##6
4. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in february##5
5. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
6. the person watching mystery movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in august##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |    4     |
| Pet         | martial-arts | drama | mystery     | satire |
| Transport   | june     | may    | february | august    |

