4. the person eating spinach is not the chef##6
5. the analyst is not the person eating radish##6
6. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person eating spinach##1
7. the librarian is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | radish        | grapefruit | tomato | spinach |
| Transport   | chef | analyst | journalist     | librarian   |

