.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-6::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, soul, house, trance
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, zinnia, marigold, azalea
1. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the fan reggae##1
2. the fan trance is not the person who growszinnia##6
3. the person who growsamaryllis is on the far right##1
4. the person who growszinnia is somewhere to the right of the person who growsazalea##5
5. the fan house is the fan house##1
6. the fan house is somewhere to the left of the person who growsamaryllis##5
7. the fan house is somewhere to the left of the fan reggae##5
8. the fan soul is somewhere to the left of the person who growsazalea##5
9. the fan soul is somewhere to the left of the person who growsazalea##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | soul | house    | reggae  | trance   |
| Nationality   | marigold  | azalea | zinnia | amaryllis |

