The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, volleyball, basketball, cycling
1. the person playing poker is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is not the person playing scrabble##6
3. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere to the right of the person playing monopoly##5
4. the person who's sport is cycling is in an even position##4
5. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
6. the person who's sport is cycling is the person playing monopoly##1
7. the person playing poker is not the person who's sport is cycling##6
8. the person playing backgammon is somewhere to the right of the person playing scrabble##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Job         | poker  | monopoly | scrabble    | backgammon |
| Transport   | volleyball | cycling | basketball | skiing  |

