.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-12::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, fonseca, vegafina, cain
4 different pets are kept: ferret, snake, turtle, goat
1. the vegafina-smoker is somewhere to the right of the owner of the turtle##5
2. the cain-smoker is not the owner of the ferret##6
3. the owner of the snake is the cain-smoker##1
4. the owner of the snake is on the right of the fonseca-smoker##1
5. the owner of the turtle is not the cain-smoker##6
6. the fonseca-smoker is not the owner of the ferret##6
7. the vegafina-smoker is somewhere to the left of the fonseca-smoker##5
8. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |   4    |
| Food        | bongani  | vegafina | fonseca | cain |
| Transport   | turtle | ferret     | goat     | snake    |

