3. the person playing snooker is not the owner of the rat##6
4. the person playing poker is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
5. the person playing chess is between the owner of the goldfish and the person playing snooker##2
6. the owner of the goldfish is not the person playing poker##6
7. the owner of the fish is on the right of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Job     | rat  | dog | fish | goldfish |
| Sport   | poker | snooker | chess   | backgammon |

