3. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
4. the blend-smoker is not the person who's birthday is in may##6
5. the person who's birthday is in march is between the person who's birthday is in may and the person who's birthday is in november##2
6. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
8. the blend-smoker is somewhere to the right of the ritmeester-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | november | march | may | july |
| Pet     | fonseca  | ritmeester      | baccarat  | blend       |

