3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
4. the person who's hobby is cooking is not the futuristic house##6
5. the wooden house is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is writing##5
6. the person who's hobby is writing is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |    2     |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | futuristic | palace | wooden      | modern   |
| Transport   | board-games  | writing   | video-games | cooking |

 